{"tid":1928247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗疫台] 建議大家建立 重用口罩 庫存","createTime":"2020-03-16T09:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T13:25:06.000Z","uid":30791,"like":6,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c16a84a5769c87528b9b44f99773eef3a1595585","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"唔知大家屋企既口罩存貨仲可以捱到幾多日<br />\n可能大家都等緊香港本地出既口罩或者等緊口罩降價<br />\n但係將來既供港口罩不見得會增加 價格亦不見得會下降<br />\n原因係世界各地開始囤積口罩 即使各地增產 亦會優先供應給各地醫療系統<br />\n因此 平民買到口罩既機會應該會下降<br />\n有見及此 我應該應該要有後備方案：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重用口罩庫存計劃綱要</span></strong><br />\n<strong>操作</strong><br />\n1. 由現在起，每日將用完的口罩脫下放入獨立的密實袋<br />\n2. 密實袋須標註日期 如在密實袋內放入紙張<br />\n3. 可以在密實袋內加入食物乾燥劑防潮<br />\n4. 寫日記 記錄每日發生既事<br />\n<br />\n如果有一天，你家中的口罩用完，<br />\n你將會有使用 重用口罩庫存的選項<br />\n<br />\n<strong>風險討論</strong><br />\n1. 現在香港確診人數非常少 亦即普遍來說口罩帶有武漢病毒的機會非常少<br />\n2. 若口罩帶有病毒 在處理口罩過程中有機會因而受感染 操作庫存前後必須做好保護措施 如洗手<br />\n3. 病毒在死物表面上能存活的時間估計為長達 9日以上<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Previously published studies have indicated coronaviruses in general &mdash; not specifically the new one &mdash; can last up to nine days on surfaces depending on the surface type, the heat, the humidity, exposure to sunlight and other factors, said Joseph Fair, a virologist, epidemiologist and NBC News Science contributor.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.today.com/health/how-long-does-coronavirus-live-surfaces-how-disinfect-kill-viruses-t175738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.today.com%2Fhealth%2Fhow-long-does-coronavirus-live-surfaces-how-disinfect-kill-viruses-t175738&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2Bebb%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=566950de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.today.com/health/how-long-does-coronavirus-live-surfaces-how-disinfect-kill-viruses-t175738</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毫無疑問 經使用過的口罩放置時間越長 上面帶有的病毒將會越少<br />\n這就是記錄日期 和寫日記的原因<br />\n當要決定使用用過的口罩時 翻查日記及新聞 評估風險才決定是否重用<br />\n<br />\n4. 當然大家會非常懷疑這種做法 如果有一日香港口罩短缺 你買唔到口罩 專家出來叫大家重用口罩的時候 你建立了庫存 就有口罩用了 而當你買到口罩 就唔需要使用庫存 抗疫成功後就可以將口罩連密實袋棄掉"},{"pid":"15ea9058f296d9887a56f55c01f031f70b659540","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNPEsEN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNPEsEN.jpg&h=b5805ab3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5d19ab79e4b050849c06918805d09bd7e3176c1","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c81b32f781a1ec7a910afb441a05c0db78a8400","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8900b6ad1953931e66be2282ab83bf3330f0a195","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T12:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954c5968ac9283b5bc930f3410b64adc1df32d36","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b96763eb856cb3c213740340df0dbbfe603ab2","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cceff032ff99417894b1e5dd013cec6e171dad3","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3c3d1bca32924ae4c05ae8fafa5ee515e6471c","tid":1928247,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mous